com.kuka.med.robotstate

Interface ITileInfo


  • public interface ITileInfo
    The ITileInfo interface provides the relevant information about the system components which are represented as tiles in the smartHMI view on the smartPAD. The relevant information are the name, level, state and error message tree of the tile. Each layer of the message tree is composed by a text and a state, as displayed on the smartHMI view. The tile level is the level of component aggregation as displayed in the Navigation bar of the smartHMI main view, e.g. Station for the Safety tile or the robot name for the Device tile.
